Crontab instructions

1. Build AdgCollector Java project using maven.
	$ mvn package

2. Create directory for addigy in user's home.
	$ mkdir -p ~/addigy

2. Move the jar file to the user's home directory.
	$ cp target/adgcollector-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar ~/addigy/

3. Register cronjob with crontab.
	$ crontab adgcollector.cron
